                    <h1 class="mr-font-family-2 top-none bottom-xs"><a class="color-gray-dark" href="http://monthlyreview.org" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Monthly Review</a></h1>
                
                
                    <small class="text-uppercase color-green profile-verified" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="bottom" title="Monthly Review has been verified by Muck Rack's editorial team.">
    <i class="fa fa-check-circle icon-left" aria-hidden="true"></i><span>Verified</span>
</small>

                
                
                    <div class="mr-font-weight-semibold">Magazine</div>
                
                
                
                    <div class="top-xs">The Monthly Review, established in 1949, is an independent socialist magazine published monthly in New York City. The publication remains the longest continuously published socialist magazine in the United States. The journal has an impact factor of 0.460. <span class="media-outlet-description-source"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Monthly_Review" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Source <i class="text-muted fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></a></span></div>
                
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

