    <h4 class="news-story-title">
        
            <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://monthlyreview.org/product/faces_of_latin_america/">Faces of Latin America</a>
        
    </h4>

<div class="row">
    
        <div class="news-story-body col-xs-12">
            <div class="news-story-byline">
                
                    
                        <a rel="nofollow" class="timeago" title="Mar 08, 2022" href="/link/oOcNO0/faces-of-latin-america">2 days ago</a>
                    
                    
                        &nbsp;|&nbsp;
                    
                
                
                    
                        


<div class="mr-byline ">
    By <a href="/duncan-green" target="_blank">Duncan Green</a>, <a href="/sue-branford" target="_blank">Sue Branford</a>
</div>


                    
                    
                
                
                    
                        &nbsp;|&nbsp;
                    
                
                



    
    
        <a href="/media-outlet/monthlyreview" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Monthly Review</a>
        
    
    


            </div>
            
            
                
                    NavigationReturn to Contentby Duncan Green and Sue Branford$16.15 – $75.00Faces of Latin America has sold more than 50,000 copies since it first appeared in 1991, and is widely considered to be the best available introduction in English to the economies, politics, demography, social structures, environment and cultures of Latin America.
                
                
            
        </div>
    
    
